Well there are two other baseball games that I would rank up there with Bad News Baseball, Baseball Simulator 1,000 and those are Base Wars (lets face it you can't beat robots beating the hell out of each other), Legends of the Diamond which has some interesting things in it like dogs running out on the field to pick up foul balls. Plus you can pick from a variable list of legends in the sport. Oh yeah, I forgot to metion that if you hit someone with a pitch or vice versa there was a chance they would charge the mound and attack the pitcher.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=122">Hamburglar</a> — Thu Apr 27, 2006 9:51 am</p><hr />
